<ol style="margin:0 0 16px 0; padding-left:20px;">

  <li style="margin:0 0 10px 0;">
    <b>Start Here</b> –
    <span style="display:block; margin-top:6px;">

      <!-- GCA -->
      <span style="display:block; margin:0 0 10px 0;">
        <span style="font-size:14px; color:#555555;">
          <em>GCA (will show when productLine = GCA)</em>
        </span><br/>

        <a href="https://globalcareeraccelerator.org/app/login">
          <b>Log in to [programName]</b>
        </a>
        and click <b>“Go to Course”</b>.

        <div style="margin-top:4px;">
          → Login email: <b>{{email}}</b>
        </div>
      </span>

      <!-- CDE -->
      <span style="display:block;">
        <span style="font-size:14px; color:#555555;">
          <em>CDE (will show when productLine = CDE)</em>
        </span><br/>

        <a href="https://hq.globaltech.org">
          <b>Log in to [lmsName]</b>
        </a>
        for <b>{{programName}}</b>.

        <div style="margin-top:4px;">
          → Login email: <b>{{email}}</b>
        </div>
      </span>

    </span>
  </li>

  <li style="margin:0 0 10px 0;">
    <b>Catch Up in [lmsName]</b> – Click [courseName] and take the tour of [lmsName].
    <div style="margin:6px 0 0 0;">
      → 1. Finish <b>[module1]</b>, <b>[module2]</b> and complete your tool setup
    </div>
    <div style="margin:4px 0 0 0;">
      → 2. Then watch the <b>[synchronousSession]</b> recording in the Media Gallery
    </div>
    <div style="margin:10px 0 0 0;">
      {{{ snippet "HQ Part Tiles" }}}
    </div>
  </li>

  <li style="margin:0 0 10px 0;">
    <b>Stay Updated</b> – Check Announcements for key info and reminders, like which [module]s to finish before the next <b>{{synchronousSession}}</b>.
  </li>

  <li style="margin:0 0 10px 0;">
    <b>Submit Work</b> – Find upcoming and previous assignment due dates on the <b>[grade]s</b> tab.
    Missed a deadline? Request an extension in the [studentChatbot] within a week.
  </li>

  <li style="margin:0;">
    <b>Plan Ahead</b> – Look on the
    <a href="{{{ snippet "link - HQ Calendar" }}}">[calendar]</a>
    to see <b>[synchronousSession]</b> dates and [assignmentName] deadlines.
  </li>

</ol>
